law.history: Repealed 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 105, sec. 77, effective July 14, 1992. -- Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 326, sec. 1, effective July 13, 1990. -- Created 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 392, sec. 3, effective April 8, 1988.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/14/92). This section was amended by the 1992 Regular Session of the General Assembly and also repealed. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
